&lt;li&gt;Design and run both inbound/inside sales and outbound BDR → AE motions, iterating rapidly to find what works.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and refine the ICP across brands and agencies; validate and evolve the go-to-market approach in close partnership with marketing and product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale the team progressively from a lean starting point to multiple layers of AEs/BDRs as results validate growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Introduce an AI-stack and modern outbound infrastructure to maximize productivity and pipeline efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with marketing, product, operations, and the Customer Success team to deliver a seamless customer journey.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide feedback on pricing, packaging, and product fit. Your voice in the room matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish clear metrics, forecasting, and reporting rhythms; manage to targets for deals closed and average deal value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;TO SHINE IN THIS ROLE 💥&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A zero-to-one mindset with “tech scrappy” energy, ideally forged at a Series A to Series C company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Genuine comfort being hands-on as a player-coach: you close deals yourself while building the team and systems around you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience leading a B2B sales team from a handful of reps to a full-scale sales org in a mid-market or similar segment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and running both inbound/inside and outbound sales motions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong cross-functional collaboration skills; you naturally partner with marketing, product, and CS to drive shared outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It would be great if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
