&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a People Operations Partner who can run the full people function for Manychat Spain — independently, confidently, and without hand-holding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a specialist role. You cover the full lifecycle, workplace operations, events, and everything in between. The measure of success is simple: people in Spain have a seamless, high-quality experience, processes are clean, and you know what&#39;s happening before it becomes a problem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What distinguishes this role:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You own the hub — not a piece of it. Everything people-related in Spain runs through you&lt;/li&gt;
