&lt;li&gt;AI is infrastructure, not optional — you build self-service and automation into your daily operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You thrive in a fast-moving, international environment. You&#39;re equally comfortable advising a manager on a sensitive termination and coordinating a team offsite. You act before you&#39;re asked.&lt;/p&gt;
